    },
    "starRating": "FIVE",
    "comment": "Buena atención, funciona el ACA y tiene servicio de Box para cambios de aceite, filtros, sin lavadero, pero con una amplia cafetería,góndolas y heladeras para llevar comida rápida, respetan bien el protocolo Covid, disponen de mesas afuera para la cafetería, y baños le ponemos un 7,50, además cuenta con vertedor de agua caliente, podes hacerte socio del ACA ahí, atienden de 9 a 16,30 hs de lunes a viernes, si sos viajero no  lo dudes.\n\n(Translated by Google)\nGood service, the ACA (Automobile Club of Argentina) is open and has a service bay for oil and filter changes. There\u0027s no car wash, but it has a large cafeteria, gondolas and refrigerators for takeaway food, they follow the Covid protocol well, they have tables outside for the cafeteria, and the restrooms are clean. We give it a 7.5 out of 10. It also has a hot water dispenser, you can become an ACA member there, they are open from 9 am to 4:30 pm Monday to Friday. If you\u0027re a traveler, don\u0027t hesitate.",
